      "url": ""
    },
    "desc": [
      "When you reach 3rd level, you augment your martial prowess with the ability to cast spells. You learn two cantrips from the wizard spell list (an additional wizard cantrip at 10th level), and three 1st-level wizard spells, two of which must be abjuration or evocation. Intelligence is your spellcasting ability. Spell save DC = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence modifier. Spell attack modifier = your proficiency bonus + your Intelligence modifier."
    ],
    "url": ""
  },
  {
    "index": "weapon-bond-eldritch-knight",
