      "name": "Eldritch Knight",
      "url": ""
    },
    "desc": [
      "You learn a ritual that creates a magical bond between yourself and one weapon. You can't be disarmed of a bonded weapon unless incapacitated. If it is on the same plane of existence, you can summon it as a bonus action, causing it to teleport instantly to your hand. You can have up to two bonded weapons, but can summon only one at a time."
    ],
    "url": ""
  },
