    },
    "desc": [
      "3rd level: ensnaring strike, speak with animals. 5th level: moonbeam, misty step. 9th level: plant growth, protection from energy. 13th level: ice storm, stoneskin. 17th level: commune with nature, tree stride."
    ],
    "url": ""
  },
  {
    "index": "channel-divinity-nature-s-wrath-oath-of-the-ancients",
    "name": "Channel Divinity: Nature's Wrath",
    "level": 3,
    "class": {
      "index": "paladin",
      "name": "Paladin",
      "url": ""
    },
    "subclass": {
      "index": "oath-of-the-ancients",
      "name": "Oath of the Ancients",
      "url": ""
    },
    "desc": [
      "As an action, you can cause spectral vines to spring up and reach for a creature within 10 feet of you that you can see. The creature must succeed on a Strength or Dexterity saving throw (its choice) or be restrained. While restrained, the creature repeats the saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a success, it frees itself and the vines vanish."
    ],
    "url": ""
  },
  {
    "index": "channel-divinity-turn-the-faithless-oath-of-the-ancients",
    "name": "Channel Divinity: Turn the Faithless",
    "level": 3,
    "class": {
      "index": "paladin",
      "name": "Paladin",
      "url": ""
    },
    "subclass": {
      "index": "oath-of-the-ancients",
      "name": "Oath of the Ancients",
      "url": ""
    },
    "desc": [
      "As an action, you present your holy symbol, and each fey or fiend within 30 feet of you that can hear you must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is turned for 1 minute or until it takes damage. A turned creature must spend its turns trying to move as far away from you as it can, and can't willingly move to a space within 30 feet of you. If the creature's true form is concealed by an illusion, shapeshifting, or other effect, that form is revealed while it is turned."
    ],
    "url": ""
  },
  {
    "index": "aura-of-warding-oath-of-the-ancients",
