      "name": "Oath of Vengeance",
      "url": ""
    },
    "desc": [
      "As an action, choose one creature within 60 feet of you that you can see. That creature must make a Wisdom saving throw, unless it is immune to being frightened. Fiends and undead have disadvantage on this saving throw. On a failed save, the creature is frightened for 1 minute or until it takes any damage. While frightened, the creature's speed is 0. On a successful save, the creature's speed is halved for 1 minute or until it takes any damage."
    ],
    "url": ""
  },
